quran[31]{c,v,t}:
  74,1,Owange ggwe eyeebikiridde (olwokutya Malayika Jiburilu lwe yakuleetera obubaka okuva eri Katonda)
  74,2,Golokoka otiise abantu ebibonerezo bya Katonda
  74,3,Ne Mukama Katondawo yekka gwoba ogulumiza
  74,4,N'engoyezo zitukuze
  74,5,Amasanamu geewalire ddala
  74,6,Tokoleranga abantu obulungi ng'ogenderera kufunamu bulungi kuno ku nsi
  74,7,Beeranga mugumikiriza osobole okufuna okusiima kwa Mukama Katondawo
  74,8,Engombe bwerifuuyibwa (kulwokuzuukira)
  74,9,Olunaku olwo lugenda kuba lunaku luzito
  74,10,Terugenda kuba lwangu eri abakafiiri
  74,11,(Owange ggwe Nabbi Muhammad) ndeka nooyo gwe nnetondera
  74,12,Nemuwa ebyobugagga ebiyitirivu
  74,13,Nemuwa nabaana abatutumufu
  74,14,Ne mugaziyiriza olugaziya (e byenfuna obukulembeze n'ekitiibwa)
  74,15,Oluvanyuma alulunkanira okumwongera okusingako awo
  74,16,Nedda sijja kumwongera kuba yawakanya ebigambo byaffe (Kur'ani)
  74,17,Nja kumussaako e bibonerezo e bizito
  74,18,Anti mazima yye (Al Walid bin Mugiira) yalowooza era naasalawo okuvvoola Kur'ani
  74,19,Nakolimirwa okusinziira ku ngeri gyeyasalawo
  74,20,Era ddala yakolimirwa ku ngeri gyeyasalawo
  74,21,Oluvanyuma yakirowozaako
  74,22,Olwo nno ne yeekaba najja emitaafu
  74,23,Ne kyaddirira ebituufu yabivaako neyekuluntaza
  74,24,Olwo nno n'alangirira nti e bigambo bya Muhammad temuli wabula ddogo erijjibwa ku balogo abasooka
  74,25,Era byayogera tebisukka ku kuba bigambo bya muntu
  74,26,"(Katonda naagamba nti:) nja kumuyingiza omuliro Sakara"
  74,27,Naye omanyi Sakara kyeki
  74,28,Gwo muliro ogutagenda kulekawo kintu wadde okukitaliza
  74,29,Gwokera ddala negusiriiza eddiba lyomuntu
  74,30,Gukuumibwa ba Malayika kkumi na mwenda
  74,31,"Ate omulimu gwokukuuma omuliro tetwaguwa okugyako ba Malayika, era omuwendo gwabwe tetwaguteekawo okugyako nga kikemo eri abatakkiriza Katonda, so nga abo abaweebwa ekitabo ekyo kibongera kukakasa (ebyo bye baalina), ate bo abakkiriza (abagoberezi ba Nabbi Muhammad) kyongera kunyweza bukkiriza bwabwe, era abaweebwa ekitabo n'abakkiriza babe nga tebasigalamu kakunkuna, wabula nga (abanafunsi) abalina obulwadde mu mitima gyabwe n'abatakkiriza bagamba nti Katonda kiki kyagenderera mu kifananyi kino, bwatyo nno Katonda abuza nalungamya oyo gwaba ayagadde, ate tewali amanyi ggye lya Mukama Katondawo okugyako yye, ebyo byonna ebyogeddwa tewali kibigendererwamu okugyako okubuulirira omuntu"